verses.text_plain: Praise ye the Lord. Blessed is the man that feareth the Lord, that delighteth greatly in his commandments.
verses.verse_html:
1Praise ye the Lord. Blessed is the man that feareth the Lord, that delighteth greatly in his commandments. ▼
▼ Praise…: Heb. Hallelujah

verses.text_plain: His seed shall be mighty upon earth: the generation of the upright shall be blessed.
verses.verse_html: 2His seed shall be mighty upon earth: the generation of the upright shall be blessed.

verses.text_plain: Wealth and riches shall be in his house: and his righteousness endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 3Wealth and riches shall be in his house: and his righteousness endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: Unto the upright there ariseth light in the darkness: he is gracious, and full of compassion, and righteous.
verses.verse_html: 4Unto the upright there ariseth light in the darkness: he is gracious, and full of compassion, and righteous.

verses.text_plain: A good man sheweth favour, and lendeth: he will guide his affairs with discretion.
verses.verse_html:
5A good man sheweth favour, and lendeth: he will guide his affairs with discretion. ▼
▼ discretion: Heb. judgment

verses.text_plain: Surely he shall not be moved for ever: the righteous shall be in everlasting remembrance.
verses.verse_html: 6Surely he shall not be moved for ever: the righteous shall be in everlasting remembrance.

tokens.text: Surely he shall not be moved

verses.text_plain: He shall not be afraid of evil tidings: his heart is fixed, trusting in the Lord.
verses.verse_html: 7He shall not be afraid of evil tidings: his heart is fixed, trusting in the Lord.

verses.text_plain: His heart is established, he shall not be afraid, until he see his desire upon his enemies.
verses.verse_html: 8His heart is established, he shall not be afraid, until he see his desire upon his enemies.

verses.text_plain: He hath dispersed, he hath given to the poor; his righteousness endureth for ever; his horn shall be exalted with honour.
verses.verse_html: 9He hath dispersed, he hath given to the poor; his righteousness endureth for ever; his horn shall be exalted with honour.

verses.text_plain: The wicked shall see it, and be grieved; he shall gnash with his teeth, and melt away: the desire of the wicked shall perish.
verses.verse_html: 10The wicked shall see it, and be grieved; he shall gnash with his teeth, and melt away: the desire of the wicked shall perish.
